{"tid":1865581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺疫情嚴峻　TWICE事務所呼籲粉絲勿接機","createTime":"2020-02-06T09:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T09:08:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b09bd3b9fb07abbc15c6a09c7b8edcb572f08ef","tid":1865581,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情愈發嚴重，不少大型活動都宣布延期或取消，韓國人氣女團TWICE原定月初在日本東京巨蛋舉行簽名會，所屬的JYP事務所已宣布宣傳活動取消。<br />\n<br />\n而JYP昨日發表聲明，指因為最近的疫情問題，已決定取消或延遲舉行大規模的活動，而為了藝人及粉絲的安全，JYP呼籲大家在藝人出境或入境時，盡量避免在機場聚集，不要去送機及接機。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本月1日是TWICE隊長志效的23歲生日，她前日透過官方Instagram上載靚相，並感謝大家的生日祝福：「多謝所有向我送生日祝福的人，你們的心意我都收到了！今天下雪了，大家要小心感冒，要注意健康！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200206/bkn-20200206025756268-0206_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200206%2Fbkn-20200206025756268-0206_00862_001.html&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=5ebcee79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200206/bkn-20200206025756268-0206_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb330a08c710467fd42e0713cf3295720d499443","tid":1865581,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/0683509a1a956cc284e309e5b93e8f29/e4c6d6ae738a619a-2b/s400x600/807c7079bd87074c8304838461b3d7cb6d805c37.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F0683509a1a956cc284e309e5b93e8f29%2Fe4c6d6ae738a619a-2b%2Fs400x600%2F807c7079bd87074c8304838461b3d7cb6d805c37.gif&h=7fb24e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwice比心心once <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde29e1502058fe16930a1395f67cf8c6c224697","tid":1865581,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/bdb7b67f7a1aa145fd051f352